  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个HDCC组织架构的流程图。最顶层是HDCC Co-Director，下面有团队成员和项目管理人员。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n13",
        "n14",
        "n15"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Co-Director是核心角色。那团队成员和Program Manager/Study Officer是什么形状？矩形还是圆角？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n14",
        "n15"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都用标准矩形吧，他们属于执行层。另外还需要一个Organization节点，表示整个机构背景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n14",
        "n15",
        "n16"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，矩形节点已设置。Organization也加上了。我发现还缺一个概念——team within an org，用来表示组织内部的团队单元，用 stadium 形状合适吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n17"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，stadium形状能体现它是一个容器概念。现在来区分一下视觉层级：Co-Director要用深蓝色边框，4px粗细，填充浅蓝。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n13"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Co-Director样式已应用。团队成员保持同色系但边框细一点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n13",
        "n14"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，团队成员也是蓝系。但Program Manager要区分开——用绿色填充，2px边框，表示协调职能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n15"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我刚才把Program Manager也做成了蓝色。现在改成绿色填充#C8E6C9，边框#00C853，2px宽度，无 dash。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n15"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "正确。最后Organization和team within an org都用紫色系，表示外部/容器概念。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n16",
        "n17"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "紫色样式已应用到Organization和team within an org。检查一下：Co-Director的stroke-dasharray需要设置吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n13",
        "n16",
        "n17"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Co-Director不需要虚线，dasharray设0。其他保持实线。整体布局用elk算法，从上到下排列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "n13",
        "layout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "全部完成。五个节点、四种样式区分、elk纵向布局。Co-Director蓝色粗框，Manager绿色，Organization和Team紫色，结构清晰。",
